---
// Hero: full-bleed warm photograph + Sigmar headline + protection gradient
const heroImg = "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1565299585323-38d6b0865b47?w=1920&q=80&auto=format&fit=crop";
---
<section id="top" class="relative isolate overflow-hidden flex items-end" style="min-height: 92svh;">
  <img
    src={heroImg}
    alt="A Hawai‘i food truck at golden hour — light from the order window, hands working inside."
    class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover -z-20"
    style="filter: saturate(1.05) contrast(1.02) brightness(0.84);"
  />
  <!-- protection gradient: top + bottom darken so headlines pop -->
  <div aria-hidden="true" class="absolute inset-0 -z-10"
       style="background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(42,26,14,0.55) 0%, rgba(42,26,14,0.10) 30%, rgba(42,26,14,0.55) 72%, rgba(42,26,14,0.92) 100%), radial-gradient(120% 80% at 20% 100%, rgba(42,26,14,0.55) 0%, rgba(42,26,14,0) 60%);"></div>

  <div class="container-x py-24 md:py-28 pt-36 md:pt-40 relative z-10 text-cream">
    <p class="eyebrow eyebrow-light fade-up">Hawai‘i Mobile Food Foundation · Papaikou</p>

    <h1 class="display-xl mb-6 max-w-[18ch] fade-up"
        style="text-shadow: 0 2px 0 rgba(42,26,14,0.35), 0 8px 28px rgba(42,26,14,0.55); animation-delay: 60ms;">
      The food is theirs.<br/>
      <span style="color: var(--color-brand-yellow);">The story is ours.</span>
    </h1>

    <p class="mb-8 max-w-[44ch] text-[19px] md:text-[20px] leading-[1.55] font-medium text-cream fade-up"
       style="text-shadow: 0 1px 12px rgba(42,26,14,0.65); animation-delay: 140ms;">
      We sit with Hawai‘i’s food-truck operators for ninety minutes — the food, the
      reasons, the rest of it. A long-form podcast, a marketing course in development,
      and the unglamorous work that goes with both.
    </p>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 fade-up" style="animation-delay: 220ms;">
      <a href="#podcast" class="btn btn-primary">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" class="h-4 w-4" aria-hidden="true" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
          <circle cx="10" cy="10" r="8"/>
          <path d="M8 7l5 3-5 3z" fill="currentColor"/>
        </svg>
        Listen to the podcast
      </a>
      <a href="#vendors" class="btn btn-ghost-light">I run a truck</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
